Program: Outlook
Title: Chinese New Year
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbr2l
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
A visit to London's Chinatown to see preparations for the forthcoming New Year. Also, Cheng Yu plays a pipa in the studio, a report on ethnic loyalties during The Africa Cup of Nations football competition in Nigeria, a look at food eaten at Chinese New Year, pet crickets' diet in China and finally, business guru Alvin Hall. Show less